CLASS QHelpIndexModel INHERIT QStringListModel

   DATA self_destruction INIT .F.

   METHOD createIndex
   METHOD filter
   METHOD isCreatingIndex

   METHOD onIndexCreated
   METHOD onIndexCreationStarted

   DESTRUCTOR destroyObject

